Name: CLOUD BASE HEIGHT
Explanation: THE HEIGHT, IN TENS OF METRES, OF THE BASE OF THE LOWEST CLOUD ABOVE THE MET STATION ALTITUDE OR MEAN DATUM PLANE (MDP). USED FOR TARGET ACQUISITION MET DATA.

Name: LOW CLOUD BASE HEIGHT
Explanation: DATA ITEMS TAKEN FROM ATP-27, ATP-34 SUPPLEMENT 1 AND ATP-47 ANNEX J.
